title: Before the Fantastic Four
description:
Collection of stories of the Fantastic Four before they received their powers.

Before the Fantastic Four: Ben Grimm and Logan
Ben Grimm is sent on a secret mission of aerial surveillance of the Soviet Union with Logan, aka Wolverine.

Before the Fantastic Four: Reed Richards
Reed is caught up in a semi-humorous archaeological adventure, very much in the vein of the Indiana Jones.

Before the Fantastic Four: The Storms
A mystical amulet leads Johnny and Sue Storm on the adventure of a life time.
